{"tid":1679342,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「飲食和理非」 正式罷食播TVB嘅餐廳","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:54:03.000Z","uid":35943,"like":203,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5861f685241be5bfc67034cae1dcdcc61af6d56d","tid":1679342,"uid":35943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"請唔好睇小官媒洗腦威力<br />\n同時為左拯救身邊一眾政治冷感人士<br />\n請大家共同罷食任何播放TVB嘅餐廳<br />\n包括無綫新聞台、翡翠台、J2等等...<br />\n<br />\n我知道在商言商，<br />\n絕無可能要求食肆明確表達政治立場，<br />\n但喺食肆內唔播放翡翠台係輕而易舉<br />\n就算唔想比錢裝收費電視，<br />\n商戶都可以選擇播RTHK或ViuTV或者唔開電視<br />\n大家都有責任去支持中立不偏頗嘅電視台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>由今日起，<br />\n我地堅決唔幫襯任何仍然播放TVB嘅食肆<br />\n就算幾好食都要忍口，直到佢地改變為止</strong></span><br />\n呢個係最基本嘅和理非行動<br />\n希望大家都可以支持"},{"pid":"c2172d00201d2263fa937c9262e3e77a47301299","tid":1679342,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"4b7571258fba3517d1039b3f67e23220bdf5f5b4","tid":1679342,"uid":35943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"35ed223f0a762212a3feec632ccb82503d11f3dd","tid":1679342,"uid":35943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b18e93aae7ef493229522ea24d14efe44412e7da","tid":1679342,"uid":35943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3230402602f264054416d7541604a982b7075e16","tid":1679342,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"唔幫襯好耐<br />\n邊個播CCTV都唔方好人"},{"pid":"9cb911bc7f78461fe57c3027546335aad5c90276","tid":1679342,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"一定要做"},{"pid":"f3bb18ec91d10d7571aa54b8dcb83d317836e4c7","tid":1679